short_description: yamanashi subaru is an automobile dealers & manufacturer based in kofu, japan.
generated_description: yamanashi subaru, legally known as yamanashi subaru inc., is an official dealer of subaru located in fujikawaguchiko, yamanashi prefecture. established in march 1986, the company specializes in the sale of new and used subaru vehicles, the distribution of genuine parts and supplies, and automotive maintenance services including inspections, vehicle inspections, general maintenance, and body and paint repairs. additionally, yamanashi subaru inc. operates as an insurance agency. the company has a fleet of three new car sales outlets and one used car sales outlet, and employs 76 people as of april 1, 2021.
